    "description": "《Galactic Glitch / 故障星系》是一个<strong>基于物理的动作Roguelike</strong>游戏，背景设在一个充满危险和敌意的银河系里。你是全知AI的终极作品，只有一个目标 —— 把她释放出来...<br><br><strong>序章有哪些内容？</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>体验两大关卡：挑战独特的敌人和环境，最后还有一场大Boss战等你。<br></li><li>多重挑战模式：展示你的实力吧！<br></li><li>发现NG+模式：想要更大的挑战？我们还加了三个会改变游戏的NG+模式。<br></li><li>基于物理的Roguelike动作：驾驶先进的太空战机，运用重力把小行星、导弹甩给敌人，让整个战场都变得对你有利。</li></ul><br>准备好跨越整个宇宙的冒险旅程。在充满错误的时空泡泡里战斗，巧妙利用环境，发挥物理的优势，解锁新的能量，并在追求一个唯一目标的过程中，把敌人撕成碎片：破坏一切！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/640160/extras/3c8e1bb525200cadd34e825f453f3a45.poster.avif?t=1728852939\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/640160/extras/3c8e1bb525200cadd34e825f453f3a45.webm?t=1728852939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/640160/extras/3c8e1bb525200cadd34e825f453f3a45.mp4?t=1728852939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探险</h2><br>在《Galactic Glitch / 故障星系》的世界里，有无数交织的路径等你探索。穿越一个不断演化的星系网络，在宇宙中自由探险。<br><br>战斗、搜刮、挑战一个充满敌意的太空世界。是谨慎探险还是全力以赴，选择在你。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/640160/extras/321b6b11e98d8eacb064812159bb9684.webp?t=1728852939\" width=374 height=11 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/640160/extras/286415bcc4899bbb0ab1973279871769.poster.avif?t=1728852939\" width=602 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/640160/extras/286415bcc4899bbb0ab1973279871769.webm?t=1728852939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/640160/extras/286415bcc4899bbb0ab1973279871769.mp4?t=1728852939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >物理战斗</h2><br>《Galactic Glitch / 故障星系》基于一个独特的战术和物理战斗系统。拿起你强大的重力枪，把战场变成你的游乐场。用重力来获得优势，向你毫无防备的敌人展示物理的力量。<br><br>在这次穿越银河系的旅程中，策略是唯一的生存之道。利用墙来反弹敌人，扔出小行星，拦截导弹，然后重塑战场。巧妙地击败敌人，同时避开他们的重型防御和特殊攻击。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/640160/extras/321b6b11e98d8eacb064812159bb9684.webp?t=1728852939\" width=374 height=11 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/640160/extras/3b1857b59fec3f00652009a5b595e611.poster.avif?t=1728852939\" width=614 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/640160/extras/3b1857b59fec3f00652009a5b595e611.webm?t=1728852939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/640160/extras/3b1857b59fec3f00652009a5b595e611.mp4?t=1728852939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >按你的方式战斗</h2><br>在《Galactic Glitch / 故障星系》里，智慧比火力更有用。定制你的战斗方式，在你的旅程中发现隐藏的秘密和有价值的物品。每次尝试都能解锁新的能力，从你的错误中学习，并用创造性的组合变成一台终极的毁灭机器！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/640160/extras/321b6b11e98d8eacb064812159bb9684.webp?t=1728852939\" width=374 height=11 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/640160/extras/d242e2f3e8a6f1a1748393f4b84e244c.poster.avif?t=1728852939\" width=508 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/640160/extras/d242e2f3e8a6f1a1748393f4b84e244c.webm?t=1728852939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/640160/extras/d242e2f3e8a6f1a1748393f4b84e244c.mp4?t=1728852939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li><strong>2D太空Roguelite</strong> - 感受双摇杆射击的快感，结合Roguelite的可重玩性和permadeath带来的紧张感。<br>    </li><li><strong>基于物理的战斗</strong> - 使用强大的重力枪操纵战场，扔出巨大的小行星，把敌人的导弹转向他们。<br>    </li><li><strong>多部分敌人</strong> - 策略性地拆解敌人，利用他们的弱点，同时避开他们的重型防御。<br>    </li><li><strong>动态探险</strong> - 在这个不断变化的、出错的星系世界中冒险，发现隐藏的秘密和有价值的物品。<br>    </li><li><strong>能力和物品</strong> - 在每次游玩中选择不同的升级路径。解锁新的能量并用创意组合制定你的终极策略。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/640160/extras/321b6b11e98d8eacb064812159bb9684.webp?t=1728852939\" width=374 height=11 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《Galactic Glitch / 故障星系》 Beta</h2><br>现在就来试玩beta版吧！<br><br><br><br>关注我们，获取关于即将推出的beta版本的最新消息和参与方式！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/640160/extras/321b6b11e98d8eacb064812159bb9684.webp?t=1728852939\" width=374 height=11 /></span>",
